documentdbr v0.7.0 (Release date: 2017-04-14)
=============================================

Changes:

* Introducing DocumentDB connection info objects to reduce the amount of code that has to be written.
  Usage should be much more convenient now. See examples for usage.


documentdbr v0.6.1 (Release date: 2017-04-14)
=============================================

Changes:

* Bugfix: upsertDocuments() not working with partitioned collections.


documentdbr v0.6.0 (Release date: 2017-04-14)
=============================================

Changes:

* Added function upsertDocuments() to upsert multiple documents via data.frame.
* Added function countDocuments() to count either all documents in a collection or certain documents
  satisfying a specified predicate.
* Added function deleteDocuments() to delete either all documents in a collection or certain documents
  satisfying a specified predicate.
* Renamed selectSingleDocument() to getDocument().
* Smaller documentation modifications.


documentdbr v0.5.1 (Release date: 2017-04-13)
=============================================

Changes:

* Bugfix: Some queries need extra escaping to work.


documentdbr v0.5.0 (Release date: 2017-04-12)
=============================================

Changes:

* Added versions of required packages.


documentdbr v0.4.0 (Release date: 2017-04-12)
=============================================

Changes:

* Added support for request-level consistency levels.
* Added support for user agent information.


documentdbr v0.3.0 (Release date: 2017-04-11)
=============================================

Changes:

* Renamed query...() methods to select...() for convenience
* Bugfix: Several bugs around partitioned collections.
* Bugfix: Cannot find function "content" if library httr is not manually loaded.


documentdbr v0.2.0 (Release date: 2017-04-11)
=============================================

Changes:

* Added querySingleDocument() function to query single documents.
* Changed output signature of function queryDocuments(). Now "(queryResult)$documents" instead of "(queryResult)$result".
* MIT license.


documentdbr v0.1.0.9000 (Release date: 2017-04-05)
==================================================

Initial version.